      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent is still remarkably present. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail has been accounted for. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a brand-new machine, sitting on a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is an investment-quality example for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
